      "  Short leg only — IS                          Sh=  7.190  CAGR=  423.3%  MaxDD=-13.16%  WR= 71.9%  n=1510\n",
      "  Long leg only — IS                           Sh=  6.858  CAGR=  386.9%  MaxDD=-16.68%  WR= 71.5%  n=1510\n",
