      "  Best IS threshold (net 10bp):  300bps -> Sh=18.262\n",
      "  Best OOS threshold (net 10bp): 75bps -> Sh=32.033\n",
      "\n",
      "  D1 return: 4.2 bps  |  D10 return: 168.1 bps\n",
