      "\n",
      "======================================================================\n",
      "  VERDICT\n",
      "======================================================================\n",
      "  Best IS Sharpe: A: 75bp baseline (19.95)\n",
      "  Best OOS Sharpe: A: 75bp baseline (37.55)\n",
      "\n",
      "  B vs A:  IS Sh -9.519  |  OOS Sh -17.746  |  MaxDD -8.77%\n",
